{"tid":2076724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"事隔9年日本憑超級電腦「富岳」擊敗美中重奪世界第一","createTime":"2020-06-23T18:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T21:26:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8c2ddeba6040b52fbb7d985abeb7f6680d5df868","tid":2076724,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T18:04:37.000Z","msg":"全球超級電腦排行榜TOP500周一（22日）宣布，由日本理化學研究所（Riken）與富士通（Fujitsu）共同研發的「富岳」（Fugaku）超級電腦，以 Arm 技術架構為基礎，在最新的專家獨立評鑑中擊敗美國與中國大陸奪冠。富士通表示，這是該公司的超級電腦「K」2011年奪冠以來，日本超級電腦再次拿下榜首。<br />\n<br />\n在超級電腦500強之中，日本的「富岳」超級電腦以每秒415千兆次浮點運算（petaflops）速度拔得頭籌，幾乎是排名第二的IBM 「頂點」（Summit）的三倍。 第三名也是美國超級電腦，中國大陸的超級電腦則分居第四和第五名。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/擊敗美中-日本超級電腦-富岳-計算速度快ibm三倍奪全球最強-102200152.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%93%8A%E6%95%97%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%AD-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6-%E5%AF%8C%E5%B2%B3-%E8%A8%88%E7%AE%97%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E5%BF%ABibm%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8D%E5%A5%AA%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7-102200152.html&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JVQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=680f7220\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/擊敗美中-日本超級電腦-富岳-計算速度快ibm三倍奪全球最強-102200152.html</a>"},{"pid":"01b8315210b76a30e50b682f9aa0eb2dfbb2b682","tid":2076724,"uid":310637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T18:54:11.000Z","msg":"中國頭五名入面攞咗兩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4da06d8654b9c27efb6204a26efac711ca2b92d","tid":2076724,"uid":343977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T21:26:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%AF%8C%E5%B6%BD%E8%BD%9F%E7%82%B8%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%25AF%258C%25E5%25B6%25BD%25E8%25BD%259F%25